OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,FMs Roome, who believes her son Jools
OL,7,FSweeney died while attempting an
OL,8,Fonline challenge, was made an MBE by
OL,9,Fthe Prince of Wales for services to
OL,10,Fchildren's online safety.
OL,12,FThe 49-year-old, from Cheltenham,
OL,13,FGloucestershire, has campaigned for a
OL,14,Fchange in UK law to give bereaved
OL,15,Fparents access to their children's
OL,16,Fsocial media accounts after their
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,FShe believes her son's social media
OL,7,Faccounts may confirm her suspicions
OL,8,Fthat it was an online challenge that
OL,9,Fwent wrong and led to his death, but
OL,10,Fshe has been unable to access them.
OL,12,FMs Roome said: "I've got a meeting
OL,13,Fwith Wes Streeting on June 2 but the
OL,14,FPM won't meet us.
OL,16,F"We handed in a letter to Downing
OL,17,FStreet and then the following day he
OL,18,Fhad a meeting with all the tech
OL,19,Fcompanies and you think 'why does he
OL,20,Fnot want to hear our lived experience?'
OL,26,@tD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,F"I don't have any other children to
OL,7,Fsave or make a difference for but I
OL,8,Fwant to share our stories to make a
OL,9,Fdifference to the children that are
OL,10,Fstill here."
OL,12,FShe claimed the tech companies "left
OL,13,Fwalking, laughing, out of Downing
OL,14,FStreet, which actually was really
OL,15,Fhurtful".
OL,17,F"All of us have lost children and to
OL,18,Fsee them sort of laughing, walking
OL,19,Fdown Downing Street when the PM won't
OL,20,Fgive us a meeting," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]tD@`OUwD@HO]yD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,FShe added she had sent a letter to the
OL,7,FGovernment in March and got a reply
OL,8,Ffrom Liz Kendall, Technology
OL,9,FSecretary, but said her request for a
OL,10,Fmeeting was "ignored".
OL,12,FWhen asked if the Prime Minister has
OL,13,Freplied to her, she said: "No."
OL,15,FIn a direct message to Sir Keir, she
OL,16,Ftold PA: "Come on PM, give us a
OL,17,Fmeeting. We don't have big lobbying
OL,18,Fbudgets to be able to do the same as
OL,19,Ftech companies but we do want to be
OL,20,Fheard, we've got powerful stories."
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@UO]uD@[OUuD@_O]xD@JOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,FMs Roome said William told her during
OL,7,Fthe ceremony on Wednesday "it's
OL,8,Fimportant, we've got so many children
OL,9,Fseeing harmful things online".
OL,11,FShe added that more needs to be done
OL,12,Fto combat "harmful algorithms, what
OL,13,Fchildren are being fed through the
OL,14,Falgorithms, the dangers from
OL,15,Fcontacting strangers online".
OL,17,FMs Roome said she has also been
OL,18,Fcampaigning to ban social media for
OL,19,Funder 16s alongside Lord Nash, a
OL,20,Fmember of the House of Lords who
OL,21,Fproposed the restriction.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@]O]tD@KOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,F"He (Lord Nash) sent me a lovely
OL,7,Fmessage this morning to say
OL,8,Fcongratulations," she added.
OL,10,FA Government spokesperson said: "Ellen
OL,11,FRoome and countless parents like her
OL,12,Fhave been powerful voices in calling
OL,13,Ffor a safer online world for children.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister shares that
OL,15,Fdetermination. As he's said before,
OL,16,Fthis is not a question of if we act,
OL,17,Fbut how.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@QO]rD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778789155
OL,3,CEllen Roome: Bereaved mum says Starmer
OL,4,C'ignored' talks request
OL,6,F"That's why we have launched a
OL,7,Fconsultation looking at everything
OL,8,Ffrom age limits and safer design
OL,9,Ffeatures to a social media ban. We've
OL,10,Falso launched pilots with hundreds of
OL,11,FUK families, and are engaging with
OL,12,Fparents, children and experts ` to
OL,13,Fensure we take the best approach."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
